sequenceDiagram
    actor Annotator as 标注员
    participant API as REST API
    participant DB as 数据库

    Annotator->>API: GET /api/tasks/{taskId}/items
    API->>DB: 查询任务文书列表
    DB-->>API: 文书列表
    API-->>Annotator: {data: [{dataId, status}]}

    Annotator->>API: GET /api/tasks/{taskId}/items/{dataId}
    API->>DB: 查询文书内容 + 已有标注
    DB-->>API: 内容 + 命题 + 关系
    API-->>Annotator: {content, propositions, relations}

    Annotator->>API: POST /api/annotations/submit<br/>{taskId, dataId, propositions, relations, isDraft}
    API->>DB: 保存命题、关系、标注快照
    DB-->>API: 保存成功
    API-->>Annotator: {code:200, message:"提交成功"}
